<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Art Gallery</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #d8b5ff; 
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .button {
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #d8b5ff; 
            background-color: transparent; 
            border: 2px solid #d8b5ff;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #d8b5ff; 
            color: white; 
        }

        .button-red {
            background: #ffffff; 
            margin-top: auto; 
            position: fixed; 
            bottom: 20px; 
            right: 20px; 
        }
        

        .description {
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .center-image {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin-top: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="description">
        <h2>About Paintings</h2>
        <p>Paintings are visual artworks created using various techniques and mediums. They often depict scenes, emotions, or ideas, and can evoke powerful responses from viewers.</p>
        <p>Explore our collection of artistic expressions and discover the beauty of paintings from different artists.</p>
    </div>

    <button onclick="window.location.href='/home_customer'" class="button button-red">View Arts</button>

   
</body>
</html>
